---
import {
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardDescription,
  CardFooter,
  CardHeader,
  CardTitle,
} from "@/components/ui/card"
let { className } = Astro.props;
---
<Card client:load className={className} >
    <CardHeader client:load underlineWidth="6rem">
        <CardTitle client:load>
            About Me
        </CardTitle>
</CardHeader>
    <CardContent client:load>
    <div class="text-text-100">
      <p class="pt-4 md:hidden">
        Solution Architect specializing in <span class="highlight">scalable systems</span> and <span class="highlight">technical leadership</span>. Expert in GraphQL, distributed systems, and AI integration. Proven track record of <span class="highlight">driving technical excellence</span> and delivering high-impact solutions.
      </p>
      <p class="hidden md:block pt-4">
        Hi there! I'm a <span class="highlight">solution architect and technical leader</span> with expertise in designing and implementing <span class="highlight">scalable, modern architectures</span>. From GraphQL APIs to AI integrations, I specialize in crafting robust solutions that drive business value. Guided by <span class="highlight">data-driven decision making and technical excellence</span>, I excel at solving complex architectural challenges. My approach combines lean principles with modern engineering practices, focusing on <span class="highlight">system optimization, technical strategy, and sustainable growth</span>.
      </p>
      <p class="hidden md:block pt-4">
        When I'm not immersed in code, I'm a roller-skating, dancing, movie-watching, rock-climbing enthusiast. This blog is my platform to <span class="highlight">share knowledge, engage in tech discussions, and keep my skills fresh</span> from the latest tech trends.
      </p>
      <p class="hidden md:block pt-4">
        I'm passionate about mentoring teams and driving architectural excellence. Whether it's designing system architectures, optimizing performance, or implementing innovative solutions, I'm committed to <span class="highlight">making a positive impact through technology</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
</CardContent>
</Card>

<style>
.highlight {
    text-shadow: 
        0 0 0px oklch(0.7,0.12,125.16),
        0 0 0px oklch(0.72,0.09,189.99),
        0 0 0.9px oklch(0.75,0.06,246.82);
    font-size: 1.075rem;
    color: oklch(0.72, 0.09, 189.99);
}
</style>